Slow-burn psychedelic ambient / neo-psychedelia instrumental;  
dreamlike, hazy, yet emotionally heavy — like walking through rain at 3 a.m. with no destination;  
no rock guitars — instead:  
• layered analog synth pads (Roland Juno, Prophet-5) — slow LFO modulation, drifting phasing, evolving over minutes, tuned to E minor with subtle microtonal detuning;  
